# üìã Network Test Script Summary

This script is a comprehensive diagnostic tool that performs various connectivity, performance, and security tests. The test suite and intensity are controlled via command-line flags.

---

## ‚úÖ **Test Categories and Descriptions**

### üîó Connectivity Tests

| **Test**             | **Function**         | **Description**                                             |
|----------------------|----------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------|
| DNS Lookup           | `dig_random`         | DNS resolution using randomized domains and DNS servers     |
| ICMP Ping            | `ping_random`        | Tests host reachability using `ping`                        |
| Traceroute           | `traceroute_random`  | Traces path to endpoints using `traceroute`                 |
| SSH Connection       | `ssh_random`         | Tests SSH access to known hosts                             |
| NTP Sync             | `ntp_random`         | Time sync validation using `chronyd`                        |

---

### üåê HTTP/HTTPS Tests

| **Test**                   | **Function**             | **Description**                                               |
|----------------------------|--------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|
| HTTP Requests              | `http_random`            | Sends HTTP HEAD requests with various User-Agent headers      |
| HTTPS Requests             | `https_random`           | Sends HTTPS HEAD requests                                     |
| HTTP Download (ZIP/TAR)    | `http_download_zip`, `http_download_targz` | Downloads test files over HTTP                         |
| HTTPS Crawl                | `https_crawl`            | Crawls HTTPS sites, following links up to a specified depth   |
| URL Response Time          | `urlresponse_random`     | Measures time taken for HTTPS responses                       |

---

### ü§ñ AI & Ad Network Tests

| **Test**       | **Function**        | **Description**                                 |
|----------------|---------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| AI URLs        | `ai_https_random`   | HTTPS requests to AI-related endpoints          |
| Ad URLs        | `ads_random`        | Requests to ad-serving domains                  |

---

### üì• File Transfer & Download

| **Test**         | **Function**     | **Description**                                           |
|------------------|------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| FTP Download     | `ftp_random`     | FTP download of sample database files                     |
| Big File Test    | `bigfile`        | Downloads a 5GB file to test max throughput               |

---

### üîê Security & Threat Simulation

| **Test**               | **Function**         | **Description**                                          |
|------------------------|----------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| Virus Sim HTTP/HTTPS   | `virus_sim_http`, `virus_sim_https` | Downloads EICAR test file to trigger AV systems     |
| IPS Trigger            | `ips`                | Sends suspicious User-Agent to trigger IPS              |
| Nmap Port Scan         | `nmap_1024os`        | Scans TCP ports 1‚Äì1024 on targets                        |
| Nmap CVE Scan          | `nmap_cve`           | Vulnerability detection via Nmap script engine           |

---

### üì∂ Streaming and Speed Tests

| **Test**        | **Function**      | **Description**                           |
|-----------------|-------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Netflix Speed   | `speedtest_fast`  | Uses `fastcli` to test via fast.com       |

---

### üîé Web Crawling

| **Test**       | **Function**     | **Description**                                      |
|----------------|------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
| Web Crawl      | `webcrawl`       | Recursive browsing from a specified starting URL     |

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è CLI Flags

| **Flag**             | **Purpose**                                                  |
|----------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| `--suite`            | Selects a test suite (`all`, `http`, `dns`, `nmap`, etc.)    |
| `--size`             | Sets test intensity: `S`, `M`, `L`, `XL`                      |
| `--loop`             | Runs tests in an infinite loop                               |
| `--max-wait-secs`    | Max interval between loop iterations (if `--loop` is used)   |
| `--nowait`           | Disables random wait between tests                           |
| `--crawl-start`      | URL to begin web crawling from                               |

---

